    <script type="text/javascript">
        function LoginPage_OnLoad() {

            document.getElementById('screenResolution').value = "'" + screen.width + 'x' + screen.height + "'";

            //focus redirection
            var loginTextBox = window.document._all("LoginTextBox");
            var LoginPanel = window.document._all("LoginPanel");
            if (typeof (loginTextBox) != 'undefined' && loginTextBox != null) {
                LoginPanel.style.display = "";
                loginTextBox.focus();
            }
        }

        var key;

        function GetRandomSalt(callback) {
            $.ajax({
                type: "POST",
                url: "LoginPage.aspx/GetRandomSalt",
                data: "{}",
                contentType: "application/json; charset=utf-8",
                dataType: "json",
                async: "true",
                success: function (randomSalt) {
                    callback(randomSalt.d);
                }
            });
        }

        function ValidateForm(sender) {
            try {
                if (!Page_ClientValidate()) {
                    window.focus();
                    return false;
                }

                sender.disabled = true;

                if (sender == document.getElementById("LoginButton")) {
                    GetRandomSalt(LoginButtonCallback);
                }
                else if (sender == document.getElementById("LoginSSOButton")) {
                    GetRandomSalt(LoginSSOButtonCallback);
                }
                else if (sender == document.getElementById("SaveButton")) {
                    document.getElementById("CancelButton").disabled = true;

                    GetRandomSalt(ChangePasswordCallback);
                }
                else if (sender == document.getElementById("AskQuestions_SubmitQuestionsButton")) {
                    document.getElementById("AskQuestions_cancelQuestionsButton").disabled = true;

                    GetRandomSalt(AnswerSecurityQuestionsCallback);
            }
                else if (sender == document.getElementById("SetupSecurityQuestions_BtnSubmit")) {
                    document.getElementById("SetupSecurityQuestions_btnCancel").disabled = true;

                    GetRandomSalt(SetupSecurityQuestionsCallback);
                }
            }
            finally {
                return false;        //ensure no postback
            }
        }

        function SwitchOffSsoValidation() {
            if (!/\S+/.test(window.document._all("LoginSSOTextBox").value) &&
                !/\S+/.test(window.document._all("PasswordSSOTextBox").value) &&
                /\S+/.test(window.document._all("NetworkSSOTextBox").value)) {
                ValidationUtil.DetachFunction("LoginSSOTextBoxValidator");
                ValidationUtil.DetachFunction("PasswordSSOTextBoxValidator");
            }
        }

        $(function () {
            if (T360.IsMSIE7OrLess()) {
                $(window).resize(function () { $('.Document').height($('.Document').parent().height()); });
                $(window).resize();
                $('.DisclaimerText').css('position', 'absolute');
            }
            if ($('td.tdLicenseAgreementFrame').length && $(window).height() <= $('td.tdLicenseAgreementFrame').height()) {
                $(window).resize(function () {
                    $('td.tdLicenseAgreementFrame > div').height(0);
                    $('td.tdLicenseAgreementFrame > div').height($('td.tdLicenseAgreementFrame').height());
                });
                $(window).resize();
            }
            if ($('td.tdCenter').length && $(window).height() <= $('td.tdCenter').offset().top) {
                $('div.accountAgreement').addClass('eqie10');
            }
        });
    </script>

        require(['globalHeader', 'bookmarkManager', 'order!jquery', 'order!t360bookmarkTree', 'underscore'], function (header, bookmarkManager) {
            // Create our tree
            $('#bookmarksMenuPanelTree').t360bookmarkTree({
                dataUrl: '/Bookmarks/GetBookmarks',
                loadDataOnCreate: false,
                onActivate: function(node) {
                    if (!node.data.isFolder) {
                        var url = node.data.url;
                        mainFrame.navigateToUrl(url);
                        header.hideAllPanels();
                        node.deactivate();
                    }
                }
            });

            // This will add our bookmark manager to the window object (YUCK! But needed so we can get to it from the legacy stuff).
            // It will also return us the bookmark manager to work with, so we don't have to get it off the window.
            var manager = bookmarkManager($('#bookmarksMenuPanelTree').data('t360bookmarkTree'), $('#bookmarksMenuPanelTree'));
            manager.rootFolderId = '416501';
            
            header.setOnLoadBookmarks(manager.loadTree);
            
            // Add our event handlers
            $('#bookmarksMenuPanelAddBookmark').off('click.t360bookmarks');
            $('#bookmarksMenuPanelAddBookmark').on('click.t360bookmarks', function () {
                if ($(this).hasClass('disabled')) return false;
                
                $.showDialog(manager.addBookmarkUrl, [manager.pageBookmarkName], {
                    width: 480, 
                    height: 300, 
                    title: 'Add Bookmark', 
                    callback: function(result) {
                        if (result == null || result === "") return;
                        
                        var results = result.split('');
                        if (results[0] === 'AddBookmark') {
                            $.post('/Bookmarks/AddLink', {
                                    folderId: results[2],
                                    title: results[1],
                                    url: manager.pageBookmarkUrl
                                }, function() {
                                    manager.reloadTree();
                                });
                        }
                    }
                });
            });
        });
    </script>

    <script>
        window.IsMainFrame = true;

        window.showCustomPrintMenu = function (links, target) {
            var dic = JsonFormatter.deserialize(links);
            var printMenu = $('#customPrintMenu');
            printMenu.empty();
            var ul = $("<ul>").appendTo(printMenu);
            for (var link in dic) {
                var li = $("<li>").css("display", "block").appendTo(ul);
                var ahref = $("<a>" + link.toString() + "</a>").attr("href", "javascript:void(0)").appendTo(li);
                var func = new Function('return this.' + dic[link]);
                var proxyFunc = $.proxy(func, target);
                ahref.on('click', proxyFunc);
            }
            printMenu.show();
            if (window.event.stopPropagation) {
                window.event.stopPropagation();
            } else {
                window.event.cancelBubble = true;
            }
        };

        window.sysToolbarInit = function (contentFrame) {
            var setupButton = function (name, funcs, uniqueId) {
                var button = $("#" + uniqueId);
                button.off('click');
                if (typeof funcs[name] === 'function') {
                    var proxyFunc = $.proxy(funcs[name], contentFrame);
                    button.on('click', proxyFunc);
                    button.show();
                } else {
                    button.hide();
                }
            };

            var contentFrameSupportsButtons = contentFrame != null && contentFrame.sysToolbarFuncs != null;
            var funcs = contentFrameSupportsButtons ? contentFrame.sysToolbarFuncs : [];

            setupButton('print', funcs, 'sysToolbarPrint');
            setupButton('email', funcs, 'sysToolbarEmail');
        };

      
        function getCountOfTabs() {
            var key = getTabCountKey();

            if (window.localStorage[key] == undefined) {
                window.localStorage[key] = 0;
            }

            return parseInt(window.localStorage[key]);
        }

        function setCountOfTabs(val) {        
            window.localStorage[getTabCountKey()] = val;
        }

        $(document).first().ready(function () {
            if (typeof (Storage) !== "undefined") {

                if (!window.sessionStorage.isLogged) {
                            
                    if (getCountOfTabs() > 0) {                    
                        window.sessionStorage.isLogged = true;
                    } else {                        
                        toolBar.logOff();
                    }
                }

                setCountOfTabs(getCountOfTabs() + 1);            
            }
        });

        $(window).first().one("beforeunload", function () {
            if (typeof (Storage) !== "undefined") {
                setCountOfTabs(getCountOfTabs() - 1);
            }
        });


        $('#DocumentIFrame').on('load', function () {
            window.IframeAfterLoadSeconds = (new Date()).getTime();
            window.IframePageLoadTimeSeconds = (window.IframeAfterLoadSeconds - window.IframeBeforeLoadSeconds) / 1000;
        });

    </script>

</title><meta content="Microsoft Visual Studio .NET 7.1" name="GENERATOR"><meta content="C#" name="CODE_LANGUAGE"><meta content="JavaScript" name="vs_defaultClientScript"><meta content="http://schemas.microsoft.com/intellisense/ie5" name="vs_targetSchema"><link href="../../Common/Themes/pageStyles/page-styles-ff.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <script language="javascript">
        var ComparedItemCount = 0;
        var Items = new Array();
        var history_array = new Array();

        function ItemToCompare(item, imageId, detail1, detail2, detail3)
        {
            this.item = item;
            this.imageID = imageId;
            this.detail1 = document._all(detail1);
            this.detail2 = document._all(detail2);
            this.detail3 = document._all(detail3);
        }

        function CreateItems()
        {
            Items[0] = new ItemToCompare(document._all('BudgetHistoryCompareID1'), 'RemoveItemImage_1', 'ItemDetail_1_1', 'ItemDetail_1_2', 'ItemDetail_1_3');
            Items[1] = new ItemToCompare(document._all('BudgetHistoryCompareID2'), 'RemoveItemImage_2', 'ItemDetail_2_1', 'ItemDetail_2_2', 'ItemDetail_2_3');
        }

        function InitializeCompareBudgetTable()
        {
            CreateItems();

            try
            {
                if (Items[0].item.value == '')
                {
                    document._all(Items[0].imageID).className = "disabled";
                    document._all(Items[0].imageID).style.cursor = "text";
                    Items[0].detail1.innerText = " ";
                    Items[0].detail2.innerText = " ";
                    Items[0].detail3.innerText = " ";
                }

                if (Items[1].item.value == '')
                {
                    document._all(Items[1].imageID).className = "disabled";
                    document._all(Items[1].imageID).style.cursor = "text";
                    Items[1].detail1.innerText = " ";
                    Items[1].detail2.innerText = " ";
                    Items[1].detail3.innerText = " ";
                }
            }
            catch (e)
            { }
        }

        function FillCompareBudgetTable()
        {
            var tags = $('#BudgetHistoryDataGrid input').toArray();

            for (var i = 0; i < tags.length; i++)
            {
                input = tags[i];

                if (input.type == 'checkbox')
                {
                    var id = input.parentElement.getAttribute('entityID');
                    
                    if (id != null)
                    {
                        input.checked = false;
                        input.disabled = false;
                    }
                }
            }
            
            var control;
            var arr;

            if (Items[0].item.value != '')
            {
                control = GetControlByBudgetHistoryID(Items[0].item.value);
                arr = getArrayValuesByEntityID(Items[0].item.value);

                if (control)
                {
                    control.checked = true;
                    AddItemCompare(Items[0].item.value, arr, false);
                }
            }
            else
            {
                ClearItem(0);
            }

            if (Items[1].item.value != '')
            {
                control = GetControlByBudgetHistoryID(Items[1].item.value);
                arr = getArrayValuesByEntityID(Items[1].item.value);

                if (control)
                {
                    control.checked = true;
                    AddItemCompare(Items[1].item.value, arr, false);
                }
            }
            else
            {
                ClearItem(1);
            }

            UpdateCompareButtonState();
        }

        function AddItemCompare(budgetHistoryId, arrayValues, updateState)
        {
            var index = ComparedItemCount;

            if (index == 1)
            {
                if (parseInt(Items[0].item.value) < parseInt(budgetHistoryId))
                {
                    Items[1].item.value = Items[0].item.value;
                    Items[1].detail1.innerHTML = Items[0].detail1.innerHTML;
                    Items[1].detail2.innerHTML = Items[0].detail2.innerHTML;
                    Items[1].detail3.innerHTML = Items[0].detail3.innerHTML;
                    document._all(Items[index].imageID).className = "";
                    document._all(Items[index].imageID).style.cursor = "hand";
                    index = 0;
                }
            }

            Items[index].item.value = budgetHistoryId;
            document._all(Items[index].imageID).className = "";
            document._all(Items[index].imageID).style.cursor = "hand";
            Items[index].detail1.innerHTML = arrayValues[2];
            Items[index].detail2.innerHTML = arrayValues[3];
            Items[index].detail3.innerHTML = arrayValues[4];
            ComparedItemCount++;

            if (updateState == null || updateState)
            {
                UpdateCompareButtonState();
            }
        }

        function ClearItem(index)
        {
            Items[index].item.value = "";
            Items[index].detail1.innerHTML = " ";
            Items[index].detail2.innerHTML = " ";
            Items[index].detail3.innerHTML = " ";
            document._all(Items[index].imageID).className = "disabled";
            document._all(Items[index].imageID).style.cursor = "text";
        }

        function RemoveItem0()
        {
            if (document._all(Items[0].imageID).className == "disabled")
            {
                return;
            }

            var control = GetControlByBudgetHistoryID(Items[0].item.value);

            if (Items[1].item.value != '')
            {
                Items[0].item.value = Items[1].item.value;
                Items[0].detail1.innerHTML = Items[1].detail1.innerHTML;
                Items[0].detail2.innerHTML = Items[1].detail2.innerHTML;
                Items[0].detail3.innerHTML = Items[1].detail3.innerHTML;
                ClearItem(1);
            }
            else
            {
                ClearItem(0);
            }

            if (control)
            {
                control.checked = false;
            }
            
            ComparedItemCount--;
            UpdateCompareButtonState();
        }

        function RemoveItem1()
        {
            if (document._all(Items[1].imageID).className == "disabled")
            {
                return;
            }

            var control = GetControlByBudgetHistoryID(Items[1].item.value);
            
            ClearItem(1);

            if (control)
            {
                control.checked = false;
            }
            
            ComparedItemCount--;
            UpdateCompareButtonState();
        }

        function UpdateCompareButtonState()
        {
            var id;
            
            if (ComparedItemCount == 2)
            {
                var tags = $('#BudgetHistoryDataGrid input').toArray();

                for (var i = 0; i < tags.length; i++)
                {
                    input = tags[i];
                    
                    if (input.type == 'checkbox')
                    {
                        id = input.parentElement.getAttribute('entityID');

                        if (id != null && !input.checked)
                        {
                            input.disabled = true;
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
            else
            {
                var tags = $('#BudgetHistoryDataGrid input').toArray();

                for (var i = 0; i < tags.length; i++)
                {
                    input = tags[i];
                    
                    if (input.type == 'checkbox')
                    {
                        id = input.parentElement.getAttribute('entityID');
                        
                        if (id != null && input.disabled)
                        {
                            input.disabled = false;
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
            
            $('#CompareButton').prop('disabled', ComparedItemCount != 2);
        }

        function GetControlByBudgetHistoryID(entityId)
        {
            var tags = $('#BudgetHistoryDataGrid input').toArray();

            for (var i = 0; i < tags.length; i++)
            {
                input = tags[i];
                
                if (input.type == 'checkbox')
                {
                    var id = input.parentElement.getAttribute('entityID');

                    if (id != null && id == entityId)
                    {
                        return input;
                    }
                }
            }
            
            return null;
        }

        function GetItemByBudgetHistoryID(entityId)
        {
            if (Items[0].item.value == entityId)
            {
                return 0;
            }

            if (Items[1].item.value == entityId)
            {
                return 1;
            }

            return -1;
        }

        function getArrayValuesByEntityID(entityId)
        {
            var arrHist = history_array;
            var i;
            var j;
            
            for (i = 0; i < arrHist.length; i++)
            {
                var arrAm = arrHist[i];

                if (arrAm[1] == entityId)
                {
                    return arrAm;
                }
            }
            
            return null;
        }

        function CompareCheckBox_OnClick(entityId)
        {
            var arrayValues = getArrayValuesByEntityID(entityId);

            if (window.event.srcElement.checked && ComparedItemCount == 2)
            {
                window.event.returnValue = false;
                
                return;
            }

            if (window.event.srcElement.checked)
            {
                AddItemCompare(entityId, arrayValues);
            }
            else
            {
                var index = GetItemByBudgetHistoryID(entityId);

                if (index == 0)
                {
                    RemoveItem0();
                }
                else if (index == 1)
                {
                    RemoveItem1();
                }
            }
        }

    </script>

    <script type="text/javascript">
        function LoginPage_OnLoad() {

            document.getElementById('screenResolution').value = "'" + screen.width + 'x' + screen.height + "'";

            //focus redirection
            var loginTextBox = window.document._all("LoginTextBox");
            var LoginPanel = window.document._all("LoginPanel");
            if (typeof (loginTextBox) != 'undefined' && loginTextBox != null) {
                LoginPanel.style.display = "";
                loginTextBox.focus();
            }
        }

        var key;

        function GetRandomSalt(callback) {
            $.ajax({
                type: "POST",
                url: "LoginPage.aspx/GetRandomSalt",
                data: "{}",
                contentType: "application/json; charset=utf-8",
                dataType: "json",
                async: "true",
                success: function (randomSalt) {
                    callback(randomSalt.d);
                }
            });
        }

        function ValidateForm(sender) {
            try {
                if (!Page_ClientValidate()) {
                    window.focus();
                    return false;
                }

                sender.disabled = true;

                if (sender == document.getElementById("LoginButton")) {
                    GetRandomSalt(LoginButtonCallback);
                }
                else if (sender == document.getElementById("LoginSSOButton")) {
                    GetRandomSalt(LoginSSOButtonCallback);
                }
                else if (sender == document.getElementById("SaveButton")) {
                    document.getElementById("CancelButton").disabled = true;

                    GetRandomSalt(ChangePasswordCallback);
                }
                else if (sender == document.getElementById("AskQuestions_SubmitQuestionsButton")) {
                    document.getElementById("AskQuestions_cancelQuestionsButton").disabled = true;

                    GetRandomSalt(AnswerSecurityQuestionsCallback);
            }
                else if (sender == document.getElementById("SetupSecurityQuestions_BtnSubmit")) {
                    document.getElementById("SetupSecurityQuestions_btnCancel").disabled = true;

                    GetRandomSalt(SetupSecurityQuestionsCallback);
                }
            }
            finally {
                return false;        //ensure no postback
            }
        }

        function SwitchOffSsoValidation() {
            if (!/\S+/.test(window.document._all("LoginSSOTextBox").value) &&
                !/\S+/.test(window.document._all("PasswordSSOTextBox").value) &&
                /\S+/.test(window.document._all("NetworkSSOTextBox").value)) {
                ValidationUtil.DetachFunction("LoginSSOTextBoxValidator");
                ValidationUtil.DetachFunction("PasswordSSOTextBoxValidator");
            }
        }

        $(function () {
            if (T360.IsMSIE7OrLess()) {
                $(window).resize(function () { $('.Document').height($('.Document').parent().height()); });
                $(window).resize();
                $('.DisclaimerText').css('position', 'absolute');
            }
            if ($('td.tdLicenseAgreementFrame').length && $(window).height() <= $('td.tdLicenseAgreementFrame').height()) {
                $(window).resize(function () {
                    $('td.tdLicenseAgreementFrame > div').height(0);
                    $('td.tdLicenseAgreementFrame > div').height($('td.tdLicenseAgreementFrame').height());
                });
                $(window).resize();
            }
            if ($('td.tdCenter').length && $(window).height() <= $('td.tdCenter').offset().top) {
                $('div.accountAgreement').addClass('eqie10');
            }
        });
    </script>
